T16TD4435E:286b-0: @286b * // 'phags pa klu sgrub kyi zhal snga nas mdzad pa'i man ngag zab mo bzhugs /
T16TD4435E:286b-2: # // srid pa gsum gyi bla ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4435E:286b-3: 'phags pa klu sgrub zhal snga nas //
T16TD4435E:286b-4: bkod par gyur pa rtsa ba'i mdzod //
T16TD4435E:286b-5: sems can kun la rjes brtse bas //
T16TD4435E:286b-6: bdag gis rab tu brjod par bya //
T16TD4435E:286b-7: ka na ka panytsanggi blangs nas aa lam bu sha dang /
T16TD4435E:286b-10: pi bi ling gi sa bon dang /
T16TD4435E:286b-11: 'di rnams kanydzi ka dang btags nas brisha na la byugs na /
T16TD4435E:286b-12: ku randa sel bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:286b-13: ma he'i mar sar dang nas kyi phye dang /
T16TD4435E:287a-1: 'di dag thams cad gcig tu byas nas nyed par byas na sbom por byed pa'i mchog go //
T16TD4435E:287a-7: n'a ga ba l'a rnams kyis nu ma mchog tu mnyes na de yis bum pa lta bur 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:287a-8: na ma: sa ba r'a nam ha ri dra sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:287a-9: so rtsi la lan bdun bsngags pa byas nas gang la byin pa de dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:287a-16: sing ldeng rnams mtshan mo bdun gyi nye bar sbyor bas ngag mi gsal ba dag par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:287a-17: byi dang ga'i snying po srang gcig / aa ru ra srang gcig / ba ru ra srang gcig dang /
T16TD4435E:287a-18: bu ram srang drug ste 'di dag mnyam pa chu dang bcas pa zos na /
T16TD4435E:287a-19: rlung nad ma lus pa sel bar the tshom med /
T16TD4435E:287a-25: so rtsi dang bcas pa bud med la byin na gzhan gyis dbang du byed par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:287a-26: skar ma rgyal la myos byed kyi 'bras bu blangs te /
T16TD4435E:287a-27: skar ma skag la shun pa dang /
T16TD4435E:287a-28: skar ma me bzhi la 'dab ma dang /
T16TD4435E:287a-29: skar ma nag pa la me tog dang /
T16TD4435E:287a-30: skar ma snubs la rtsa ba rnams blangs te /
T16TD4435E:287a-31: 'di rnams phye mar byas nas sbrang dang lhan cig ril bu byas te /
T16TD4435E:287a-32: ras kyis bcings (ba sa na tso) nas dril ba rdungs nas phye mar byas te /
T16TD4435E:287a-33: so rtsi dang mnyam du gang la byin pa de thams cad mod la dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:287a-34: hr'im ghrum bi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:287a-35: sngags 'di 'dab ma la bris nas gang la byin pa de'i nyin gcig pa dang /
T16TD4435E:287a-38: rims mi bzad pa sel bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:287a-39: na mo ratna tra y'a ya /
T16TD4435E:287a-40: na ma aary'a ba lo ki te shva r'a ya /
T16TD4435E:287a-43: ma h'a k'a ru ni k'a ya /
T16TD4435E:287a-46: bi ka re stam bha ni bi ka re stam bha ni /
T16TD4435E:287a-47: sarba ro ga pra sha ma ni sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:287b-0: sngags 'di lan @287b nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas te /
T16TD4435E:287b-2: gos la mdud pa byas nas rgyal po'i pho brang du zhugs na rgyal po khros pa rab tu dang bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:287b-3: ba lang gi so dang bya rog gi brun mnyam par btags te /
T16TD4435E:287b-4: gang gi mgo la gtor ba de thams cad dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:287b-7: gang gi khyim du bzhag na de skrod par byed do //
T16TD4435E:287b-8: s'a kho ta ka'i rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-9: ba ru ra'i rtsa ba gcig tu byas nas gang gi khyim du bzhag na de'i khyim du rtag tu 'thab mo 'byung ngo //
T16TD4435E:287b-18: rgya spos kyi rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-20: 'di dag thams cad chu la btags te mig sman byas na /
T16TD4435E:287b-21: rab rib ma lus pa sel bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:287b-22: w'a ku dzi k'a bri gang dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-24: ra'i 'o ma cha mnyam pa byas nas /
T16TD4435E:287b-25: ba lang gi chu dang mnyam par sbyar te zangs kyi snod du bzhag nas /
T16TD4435E:287b-26: de lus la dril phyi byas na mdze nad ma lus pa sel bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:287b-29: de bzhin du skyu ru ra'i 'bras bu dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-31: khu ba des bsgos nas nyi ma la bzhag ste /
T16TD4435E:287b-32: slar yang w'a gu dzi k'i' phye ma zhog gang byas nas dkrugs te /
T16TD4435E:287b-33: rgas pa'o ma'i bza' ba dang lhan cig zos na zhag bdun gyis mdze nad sel par byed do //
T16TD4435E:287b-34: de yang gal te las kyi dbang gis na mi 'grub po //
T16TD4435E:287b-35: de bzhin du skyu ru cha bcu dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-36: byi tang ga cha lnga dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-37: aa ru ra cha bcu dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-38: tsi tra ka cha lnga dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-39: w'a gu dzi cha bdun dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-41: ra mo shag cha dgu dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-42: til mar bsres pa zla ba gcig gis skra dkar 'joms so //
T16TD4435E:287b-43: 'di ni byug pa mdor bsdus pa'o //
T16TD4435E:287b-44: bye'u khanydza r'i ta'i rus pa dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-45: sbrul gyi mgrin pa'i bags pa dang /
T16TD4435E:287b-46: shing gang la sbyin pa'i bdug pa de shing de'i drung du mnyam par dor ro //
T16TD4435E:288a-0: bye'u khanydza r'i ta'i sha dang sbrang rtsi @288a * //
T16TD4435E:288a-2: bya ba'i dus su skye gnas la byugs te /
T16TD4435E:288a-3: bud med gang la skyes bu mngon par bsgrod par byed na de dang po bzhin du skyes pa de'i bur 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288a-4: dgon pa'i 'ug pa bzung nas de'i mig dang pi pi ling gis byugs te /
T16TD4435E:288a-5: de'i rdul lhung bas mig la mig sman byas na /
T16TD4435E:288a-6: de sbas pa de mi mthong ngo //
T16TD4435E:288a-7: s'a p'i ti ta by'a dha tra ro pannam pra yatstshati /
T16TD4435E:288a-13: shing mngar rnams mnyam par sbyar te /
T16TD4435E:288a-14: gdong la dril phyi byas na /
T16TD4435E:288a-16: rkang pa dag padma'i 'dab ma lta bur 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288a-17: bud med thams cad rgyal po'i pho brang du mdzes shing sdug par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288a-18: yang shing mngar dang btags te ril bu sbyar nas chu'i bum par bcug na /
T16TD4435E:288a-20: aom ma h'a ba li ja ye sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:288a-21: gos la yongs su bzlas te bsgos na skal ba bzang por 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288a-22: rig pa 'dzin pas spre'u'i mjug ma blangs te sbrang dang btags nas lte ba'i phyogs su byugs na ling ga gyen du 'gyur bar the tshom med do //
T16TD4435E:288a-26: pandi ta ga ra'i rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4435E:288a-27: srin lag gi khrag rnams mnyam par sbyar te /
T16TD4435E:288a-28: dur khrod kyi thal ba dang 'di dag sbyar bas skyes pa dang bud med dbang du byed do //
T16TD4435E:288a-34: 'di dag cha mnyam par byas nas til mar gyis smin par byas pa'i til mar des /
T16TD4435E:288a-35: lingga nyed par byas na sbom par byed pa'i mchog tu 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288a-39: nirma la cha mnyam par phye mar byas nas gang la byin pa de dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288b-0: bu ram sbyar bas bdug pa byas nas bdag nyid rgyal po'i pho brang du song na mchod pa chen po thob @288b cing btsun mo rnams kyis dri snom par byed do //
T16TD4435E:288b-1: bye'u khanydza r'i ta'i brun blangs te /
T16TD4435E:288b-2: si ri sa'i sa bon byugs pas 'chi ba sel to //
T16TD4435E:288b-8: bdag nyid kyi khu ba sbyar te gang la byin pa de dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288b-9: shu dag dkar po'i rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4435E:288b-10: gi wang lhan cig btags te de'i thig le byas nas gang la bltas pa de dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288b-12: sbrang rtsi lhan cig btags te ril bu byas nas gang la so rtsi dang lhan cig byin pa de dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:288b-13: aom b'a ra sya mu kham drisht'a b'a larka sa ma te dza s'a /
T16TD4435E:288b-14: tsa turtha kamma h'a ghor ma kshi pra me ba bra ta sya ti /
T16TD4435E:288b-15: sngags 'di gro ga'i 'dab ma la bris te lag pa la btags na rims nyin bzhi pa phral du nyams par byed do //
T16TD4435E:288b-16: b'a gu dzi ka'i 'bras bu'i phye ma dar ba dang lhan cig btags nas de dril te /
T16TD4435E:288b-18: skyur ba thams cad dang lhan cig zos na gzhang 'brum dang /
T16TD4435E:288b-22: mtshan bar rdol ba dang dug rnams sel bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:288b-23: b'a gu dzi ka'i 'bras bu dar ba dang lhan cig btags nas de dril bas mdze thams cad dang /
T16TD4435E:288b-24: bi tsartsi ka la sogs pa sel bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:288b-25: p'a gu dza ga bre gang dang /
T16TD4435E:288b-26: seng [?] ldeng zho gang mnyam par byas te /
T16TD4435E:288b-27: chu bre brgyad dang bskol bar bya'o //
T16TD4435E:288b-28: de ni cha phyed lus pa na btungs te /
T16TD4435E:288b-34: bdag nyid kyi khrag dang mnyam par sbyar bas shing yang dbang du byed do //
T16TD4435E:288b-35: aom pi sh'a ts'i r'u be n'a ling+ga ya tsumba ya /
T16TD4435E:288b-36: bha gam sanytse yanya sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:288b-37: sngags kyi tshig 'di chu khyor ba gang la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas te nyal ba'i dus su rig ma gang gi ming smos nas btab na /
T16TD4435E:288b-38: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gis mi'i dbang po'i btsan mo yin na'ang dbang du 'gyur na gzhan lta ci smos /
T16TD4435E:288b-40: karmar ngaga'i rtsa ba dang sihya'i lo ma dang /
T16TD4435E:289a-0: @289a * // 'di dag mnyam par byas rkang pa'i mthil la byugs na sa bon 'ching bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:289a-6: sa kha sya nangga pra ma do m'a n'am t'a ye pashti sa si kham ka ro ti /
T16TD4435E:289a-7: aom ra tsandi ma h'a dand'a ya sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:289a-8: sngags 'dis bdun du mngon par bsngags nas gos la sogs par mdud pa byas na bya ba ma lus pa 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:289a-9: na ma:s'akshi:ka p'a la m'a li th'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:289a-10: gzhan yang byi la'i khrag blangs nas /
T16TD4435E:289a-12: padma'i skud pas sdong bu byas nas dbang phyug gi mdun du dud pa 'chags bar byas te mig la byugs pa tsam gyis mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:289a-14: sngags 'dis chu dkrugs te mig la byugs na the tshom med par grub par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:289a-16: ce spyang gi mkhris pa dang /
T16TD4435E:289a-18: 'di dag cha mnyam pa'i phye ma zhib mor byas te /
T16TD4435E:289a-19: rgyu skar nabs so la btags te /
T16TD4435E:289a-20: mig la byugs na mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:289a-21: s'a la parni lag pa la bcings nas /
T16TD4435E:289a-22: sa ma re k'anta zlog par byed do //
T16TD4435E:289a-23: na mashtsanda badzra p'a na ye ma h'a yaksha se n'a pa ta ye /
T16TD4435E:289a-24: tadya th'a aom badzra hri ksh'i sphat /
T16TD4435E:289a-25: rig sngags 'di lan cig brjod cing /
T16TD4435E:289a-26: aom sam tso ram stam bha ya sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:289a-27: k'a la simbi ka'i rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4435E:289a-30: 'di dag cha mnyam bar byas nas /
T16TD4435E:289a-31: chu dang btags te ril bu byas nas grib ma la bskams te /
T16TD4435E:289a-32: ril bu de la yang dag par reg pa'i skyes bu'i lag pa g-yas par padma 'dab ma brgyad pa kun nas bris te /
T16TD4435E:289a-33: lag pa des bud med kyi lag pa g-yas pa bzung na bud med de mod la dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:289a-34: dri bzang chen po'i rtsa ba rked la bcings na khu ba rengs par byed pa'i mchog tu bstan no //
T16TD4435E:289a-35: ba r'a ha k'anta'i rtsa ba chu dang btags te rkang pa'i mthi la la byugs na khu ba rengs par byed do //
T16TD4435E:289a-36: na ma:sarba sidha bhya: sidherbha ba tra me sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:289b-5: musta ka ste thams cad gcig tu cha mnyam par byas nas /
T16TD4435E:289b-6: zhib tu btags te bud med kyi mgo la bsnun na ;
T16TD4435E:289b-8: na ma: krishna sarba r'a ya ma sa k'a n'am kundam bamdh'a mi sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:289b-9: ji srid nyi ma shar gyi bar du /
T16TD4435E:289b-10: aom raksha raksha raksha sv'a h'a /
T16TD4435E:289b-11: sngags 'dis chu khyor ba gang la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas te /
T16TD4435E:289b-13: sbrang bu rnams skrod par byed do //
T16TD4435E:289b-14: ka ra b'i ra dmar po'i rtsa ba la lan bdun bsngags te bud med kyi mdun du gtor na bud med de'i mod kho na la dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:289b-17: lo ma rnams sbrang dang lhan cig btags nas ling+ga la byugs nas 'dod pa byas na bdag po gzhan 'dod par mi byed do //
T16TD4435E:289b-18: pa tsa ka'i mig blangs nas dz'a ti dang sundha dang lhan cig gcig tu byas nas phye ma des mig sman byas na /
T16TD4435E:289b-20: be tsa ka'i snum blangs nas ba'i mar dang lhan cig gcig tu byas nas dud pa dbab par bya'o //
T16TD4435E:289b-21: des mig sman byas nas 'byung po dang sha za rnams kyi dbus su rtse bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:289b-22: be tsa ka'i snying blangs nas chang dang lhan cig lus la byugs nas 'dod pa spyad na bud med thams cad skyes pa'i dbang du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:289b-23: tshangs pa'i shing gi rtsa ba khar bcug na khu ba rengs par byed do //
T16TD4435E:289b-35: ku ta rnams chang dang btags te /
T16TD4435E:289b-36: phra h'a ro sthi te na /
T16TD4435E:289b-37: aa shesh'a dzi rn'a tarbha b'a shvarya ro bya: thams cad nyams par byed do //
T16TD4435E:289b-38: gang zhig su nthi bcu gnyis 'thungs //
T16TD4435E:289b-39: bad kan tshogs ni 'joms byed cing //
T16TD4435E:289b-40: rlung yang nye bar 'dren par byed //
T16TD4435E:289b-41: aa dzirna dzir sarya su p'i ha mashto da ka ni sam /
T16TD4435E:289b-42: (rang dga' ba/)...aa dza mo da tsha ba gsum//
T16TD4435E:290a-0: @290a * // rgyam tsha zi ra rnam gnyis dang //
T16TD4435E:290a-1: shing kun cha brgyad mnyam par bzung //
T16TD4435E:290a-2: 'di yi phye ma mar sar dang //
T16TD4435E:290a-3: skye bo gang zhig za byed pa //
T16TD4435E:290a-4: rlung gi nad ni sel bar byed //
T16TD4435E:290a-5: m'u la ma yastu bu na bhu ba ya: bi ba ti kshi ra na ba pra tya tsurnantcha sya gu do sa ma hi ta ba to dz'i rne ya shashta si na:h'i n'am gonyapi sa dznya ya tonyartsi ta p'i l'am ham sendra kunbha pra bham /
T16TD4435E:290a-6: m'a so ni bardhi ra sh'u barsha ba ya s'a mu ksho dza r'a by'a dhi bhi:aa ru ra srang gcig / ba ru ra srang gcig / skyu ru ra srang gcig / tsi tra ka srang gsum /
T16TD4435E:290a-7: lga srang gcig / pi pi ling srang gcig / na le sham srang gcig / n'a ga ge sar gyi phye ma zho bzhi /
T16TD4435E:290a-8: pho ba ris dkar po zho do //
T16TD4435E:290a-11: 'di dag thams cad phye ma zhib mor byas nas bu ram srang lnga bcu rtsa lnga dang bsres te gang gis zos pa de me stobs su 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:290a-13: mdze nad bco brgyad nyams par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:290a-23: dug nad sel bar byed do //
T16TD4435E:290a-24: de bzhin du brtan pa dang g-yo ba 'ang ngo //
T16TD4435E:290a-25: stobs glang po che dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:290a-27: zla ba gcig gis mer 'gyur ro ;
T16TD4435E:290a-28: ; rna ba phag lta bur 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:290a-29: mig bya rgod lta bur 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:290a-30: 'di thams cad kyis mi 'phrogs par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4435E:290a-31: 'phags pa rgyal ma zhes bya ba'i ril bu yongs su rdzogs so//
